Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.99,0:00:43.58,drago,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\pos(1034,549)}Překlad: Sayoko
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.66,0:00:47.91,drago,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\pos(255,222)}Korektura: May
